as Real Madrid routed Racing Santander for its second straight
6-1 home victory in Spanish soccerâ€™s Primera Liga.  Gonzalo Higuain and Mesut Ozil also scored at the Bernabeu
stadium as Real remained unbeaten under first-year manager Jose
